Ex-BBNaija ‘LockDown’ housemate, Erica Nlewedim aka Star girl has addressed speculation of being romantically involved with a popular footballer. In 2021, allegation claiming Star girl was dating an undisclosed footballer hit several social media platforms. Though, the reality TV star had been silent on the matter, she decided to address the speculation in a recent Twitter Space where she had time to chat with fans.   Countries that have qualified for 2022 World Cup     Buhari names Uzodimma, others Council members of…     Ex-Commissioner excited as Tinubu visits Gov Yahaya Bello   After a fan queried her about the allegation, Erica expressed utmost displeasure vehemently denying such ever having happened. She insisted she wasn’t in a relationship with any footballer nor does she desire to date one adding the rumour was causing her harm seeing it has gone on for a long time, attracting to her a lot of trolls. According to her: “It’s causing problems for me, attacking me for dating a footballer. I don’t know who this footballer is and it has gone on for one year. Please I don’t Know any footballer and I’m not interested in any footballer.”